# ==============================================================================
# Consolidated .gitignore for 7. Semester
# ==============================================================================

# Python & Jupyter
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.ipynb_checkpoints/
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Project Data Outputs (Timestamped Folders)
**/202[0-9]-*
**/202[0-9]_*
**/Run_202[0-9]-*

# Result & Output Folders (Ignore everything inside)
**/Angepasste_Datenbanken/
**/MiniSom_Results/
**/IntraSom_Results/
**/Kartierung/
**/Zwischenst*nde/

# Large & Binary Files (Global Ignore)
*.csv
*.pdf
*.zip
*.pkl
*.h5
*.pt
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.docx
*.doc
*.url
*.asc
*.tmp
*.html
*.pth
~$*

# Whitelist: Source Data Folders (Allow everything inside these)
!**/Gesammelte_Datenbanken/**
!**/GLiM-Kartierung/**

# General Exceptions
!**/README.md
!**/*_Mapping.csv

# Specific Notebook Output Issues
**/Preprocessed_SOM_Ready.csv
**/Synthetic_Hydrogeochemistry_Data_Imputed.csv

# Antigravity / Bot
.antigravity/
.gemini/
